These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, metal, trance
City: marseilles, london, prague
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, mystery, scientific
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, snowmobile, bike
1. the fan of metal is between the person traveling to marseilles and the person driving the trike##2
2. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
4. the fan of trance is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
5. the fan of metal is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
6. the person traveling to marseilles is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |
| Music-Genre          | blues      | metal        | trance     |
| City         | prague | london | marseilles    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery   | musical       | scientific |
| Transport         | trike  | snowmobile      | bike    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-2::.
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, domino, chess
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, disaster, thriller
House: art-deco, cottage, victorian
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, bluemaster, blend
1. the person watching action movies is on the left of the havana-smoker##1
2. the person watching disaster movies is the person playing domino##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the left of the art-deco house##1
4. the person playing domino is on the left of the cottage house##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
6. the person playing chess is in an even position##4
7. the blend-smoker is between the person watching disaster movies and the person playing mah-jongg##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3      |
| Game           | domino    | chess | mah-jongg |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | action       | thriller   |
| House           | victorian  | cottage   | art-deco     |
| Cigar         | bluemaster | blend       | havana   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-3::.
There 3 different types of food: carrot, cranberry, watermelon
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, electronic, house
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: poppy, balloon-flower, tulip
House: colonial, ranch-style, wooden
1. the person who growstulip is on the right of the colonial house##1
2. the person eating watermelon is the wooden house##1
3. the person eating cranberry is on the left or right of the person who growspoppy##3
4. the person eating carrot is between the fan of electronic and the wooden house##2
5. the fan of funk is in an even position##4
6. the person who growstulip is the person eating cranberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3     |
| Food          | watermelon | carrot | cranberry |
| Music-Genre   | house     | funk | electronic |
| Flower           | balloon-flower       | poppy   | tulip    |
| House     | wooden      | colonial   | ranch-style |

