.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-4::.
City: paris, hamburg, rome
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, hot-chocolate, fanta
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, martial-arts, mystery
There are 3 different favourite colors: chestnut, ivory, azure
1. the person traveling to paris is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
2. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
3. the person drinking fanta is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
4. the person who likes ivory is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
6. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
7. the person traveling to rome is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |      3      |
| City         | hamburg  | paris       | rome |
| Beverage           | fanta     | hot-chocolate      | milk   |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | documentary | mystery     |
| Color   | chestnut      | azure   | ivory     |

