.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-5::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: horror, thriller, crime
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, skiing, surfing
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: pop, salsa, soul
There 3 different types of food: eggplant, zucchini, lettuce
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
2. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
3. the person who's sport is rugby is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the fan of pop##1
5. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
6. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
7. the person eating lettuce is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3        |
| Movie-Genre      | crime     | thriller   | horror         |
| Sport           | rugby | skiing | surfing |
| Music-Genre   | soul      | salsa   | pop            |
| Food   | zucchini   | lettuce  | eggplant         |

