.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-6::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, tram, bike
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: gospel, electronic, blues
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, november, december
There are 3 different nationalities: dutch, italian, mexican
1. the person who's birthday is in november is between the fan of electronic and the person driving the tram##2
2. the dutch is the person driving the trike##1
3. the person who's birthday is in december is the italian##1
4. the italian is on the left of the fan of blues##1
5. the dutch is in an even position##4
6. the dutch is on the right of the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |      3      |
| Transport          | bike    | trike     | tram |
| Music-Genre           | electronic | blues | gospel      |
| Birthday   | december      | november       | march    |
| Nationality   | italian      | dutch         | mexican     |

