3. the victorian house is the person driving the roller##1
4. the colonial house is on the left or right of the cottage house##3
5. the person who growsrose is on the right of the cottage house##1
6. the oliveros-smoker is between the person driving the roller and the person who growsazalea##2
7. the person driving the taxi is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Flower          | azalea | lily | rose |
| House   | colonial  | cottage    | victorian |
| Cigar   | bongani  | oliveros   | havana    |
