.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-8::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate, soy-milk
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, chaman, siglo
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: techno, d&b, rock
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, march, october
1. the fan of rock is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far right##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
5. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
6. the person who's birthday is in august is in an odd position##4
7. the bluemaster-smoker is between the fan of d&b and the person who's birthday is in october##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | coffee    | soy-milk  |
| Cigar         | siglo        | bluemaster   | chaman   |
| Music-Genre   | rock       | techno    | d&b |
| Birthday     | october          | march | august       |

