3. the davidoff-smoker is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
4. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1
5. the prince-smoker is on the left or right of the davidoff-smoker##3
6. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
7. the davidoff-smoker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |
| Food          | apricot  | cabbage   | lemon      |
| Game   | domino    | backgammon      | mah-jongg      |
| Cigar   | alhambra | prince | davidoff    |
| City           | marseilles   | miami     | san-francisco |

