.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-11::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, documentary, satire
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, april, january
3 different pets are kept: turtle, rat, cat
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, snowboarding, volleyball
1. the person who's birthday is in april is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in april is the owner of the turtle##1
3. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
4. the person watching satire movies is in an odd position##4
5. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
6. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
7. the person who's birthday is in january is the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |      3       |
| Movie-Genre      | satire     | documentary      | epic  |
| Birthday          | april     | january | december       |
| Pet   | turtle  | cat    | rat      |
| Sport         | volleyball | badminton  | snowboarding |

