.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-12::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, november, december
There 3 different types of food: cabbage, strawberry, mango
3 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, horse
3 different games are played: chess, snooker, whist
1. the person playing whist is in an even position##4
2. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
3. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1
4. the person eating mango is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
6. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the person playing whist##1
7. the person who's birthday is in november is between the person who's birthday is in september and the owner of the bird##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Birthday      | december       | november   | september |
| Food   | cabbage | mango     | strawberry |
| Pet           | bird      | chinchilla | horse    |
| Game         | snooker  | whist     | chess |

