.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-13::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, aristoff, ritmeester
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, indian, polish
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, march, december
There are 3 different favourite colors: fuchsia, lavender, yellow
1. the montecristo-smoker is on the left or right of the aristoff-smoker##3
2. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
3. the aristoff-smoker is in an even position##4
4. the polish is on the far right##1
5. the person who's birthday is in september is the person who likes yellow##1
6. the indian is in the middle##1
7. the person who likes lavender is on the far left##1
8. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
9. the indian is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Cigar           | montecristo | aristoff   | ritmeester |
| Nationality   | argentine  | indian    | polish    |
| Birthday         | march    | september | december   |
| Color     | lavender  | yellow     | fuchsia  |

