.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-14::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, may, february
City: miami, marseilles, boston
3 different games are played: go, scrabble, domino
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, parkour, rowing
1. the person playing go is the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
3. the person who's sport is climbing is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's sport is parkour is between the person traveling to boston and the person who's birthday is in april##2
5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
6. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |      3       |
| Birthday         | february    | may   | april      |
| City           | boston | miami    | marseilles |
| Game   | go       | scrabble | domino      |
| Sport         | rowing         | parkour   | climbing     |

