.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-16::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: writing, hiking, filmmaking
The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, bartender, photographer
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, september, december
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, helicopter, jet-ski
1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far right##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is the person who's birthday is in september##1
5. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far right##1
6. the dressmaker is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
7. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3
8. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the bartender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |     3      |
| Hobby          | hiking     | writing   | filmmaking     |
| Job   | photographer   | bartender   | dressmaker      |
| Birthday   | september | june | december    |
| Transport     | jet-ski  | boat   | helicopter |

