3. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
4. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the far left##1
5. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
6. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |
| City          | edinburgh     | hannover | san-francisco   |
| Movie-Genre         | horror   | spy | disaster |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | lemonade       | juice   |
| Transport     | train     | snowmobile  | taxi        |

