.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-20::.
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, colombian, australian
House: townhouse, craftsman, ranch-style
3 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, horse, mouse
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, june, november
1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
2. the owner of the mouse is in an odd position##4
3. the ranch-style house is on the left of the colombian##1
4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
5. the australian is on the left or right of the argentine##3
6. the australian is on the right of the craftsman house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2        |     3      |
| Nationality           | argentine  | australian | colombian   |
| House   | craftsman | ranch-style           | townhouse      |
| Pet           | mouse   | horse          | guinea-pig |
| Birthday     | february    | november           | june |

 